Name: Apple menu

Synonyms: apple menu

Type: glossary

Description:
The leftmost <menu> in the <menu bar> on <Mac OS> and <OS X|OS X
systems>. 

On <Mac OS|Mac OS systems>, the Apple menu contains the current
application's About <menu item>.

References: menu bar (glossary), Mac OS (glossary), menu item (glossary),
OS X (glossary), menu (glossary)

